    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Esral'sa'Nikto, or \"mountain nikto\", adapted to the variable climate of the mountains of Kintan. They have large facial fins which are used for heat regulation. These fins also improve the esral'sa'nikto's hearing. Their skin is blue-gray, and they have neither horns nor breathing tubes, though they do have a covered nose similar to the kajain'sa'nikto.</p>",
